<body>
<%- include("navbar") %>
<div class="shipping-container">
  <h1>Shipping Information</h1>

  <p>At DealDriven, we are committed to delivering your orders quickly and safely. Below is everything you need to know about our shipping process:</p>

  <h2>1. Shipping Methods</h2>
  <p>We offer multiple shipping options to suit your needs, including standard and express delivery. Shipping charges may vary based on location and delivery speed.</p>

  <h2>2. Delivery Time</h2>
  <p>Estimated delivery times are as follows:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Standard Delivery: 5-7 business days</li>
    <li>Express Delivery: 2-3 business days</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Delivery times may vary depending on your location and any unforeseen circumstances.</p>

  <h2>3. Tracking Your Order</h2>
  <p>Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email. Use this number to track your shipment and get real-time updates on its status.</p>

  <h2>4. International Shipping</h2>
  <p>Currently, we only ship within India. We are working on expanding our delivery services to international locations soon.</p>

  <h2>5. Shipping Issues</h2>
  <p>If your order is delayed, lost, or damaged during transit, please contact our customer support team immediately. We will assist you in resolving the issue promptly.</p>

  <h2>6. Packaging</h2>
  <p>All products are carefully packaged to ensure they arrive safely. We use sturdy packaging materials to protect your items during shipping.</p>

</div>
<%- include("footer") %>
</body>
